main: ^Intramuros is known as the walled city of the Philippines. It is located at the mouth of Pasig River in Manila, Philippines.

c-0: ^The walled city was built some 400 years ago and it can be best enjoyed by walking and/or biking. The city is comprised of a century old district having its church, school, hospital, and a residential area.
^When our national hero Dr. Jose Rizal was arrested, he was imprisoned here. He was then executed in Luneta Park located just outside Intramuros.
